			     DNSSEC-Tools
			Is your domain secure?


This directory contains documentation for the validator.

* libval.pod
	Man page in POD format for the interfaces exported by 
	the core validation library namely,
	resolve_n_check(), free_query_chain(), free_assertion_chain(),
	free_result_chain(), get_context(), destroy_context(), 
	switch_effective_policy(), p_val_error().

* val_gethostbyname.pod:
	Man page in POD format for the val_gethostbyname(),
	val_x_gethostbyname(), val_get_hostent_dnssec_status(),
	val_duphostent() and val_freehostent() functions of the
	validator API.

* val_getaddrinfo.pod:
	Man page in POD format for the val_getaddrinfo(),
	val_x_getaddrinfo(), val_get_addrinfo_dnssec_status(),
	val_dupaddrinfo() and val_freeaddrinfo() functions of the
	validator API.

* val_query.pod:
	Man page in POD format for the val_query() and val_x_query()
	functions of the validator API.

